---
import Grid from "./Grid.astro";
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="section with-background bg-variant project-highlights">
    <header class="section-header stack gap-1 lg:gap-2">
        <h3>Achievements & Projects</h3>
    </header>
    <div class="gallery">
        <Grid variant="small">
            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="rocket-launch" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>Platform Engineering Enablement</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    iptiQ (Swiss Re) · DevEx · DevOps · Leadership
                </p>
                <p>
                    Founded and led the company's Platform Engineering team,
                    focusing on DevEx and DevOps. Accelerated delivery and
                    reduced onboarding time while raising quality standards by
                    centralizing processes, tooling, and technology best
                    practices.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="ai" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>AI-Powered Email Processing</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    iptiQ (Swiss Re) · AI Integration · AWS Bedrock
                </p>
                <p>
                    Integrated with AWS Bedrock to categorize incoming emails
                    from AWS SNS and trigger automated workflows. This AI
                    integration reduced task execution time from ~7 minutes to
                    just ~15 seconds, delivering a step-change in efficiency.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="trend_down" size="1.2em" color="green" />
                    </span>

                    <h4>Ephemeral Test Environments</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">iptiQ (Swiss Re) · AWS · GitLab CI</p>
                <p>
                    Reduced E2E testing costs from ~€6,000 to ~€350/month and
                    cut cycle time from ~4h to ~40m by introducing automated,
                    on-demand ephemeral environments.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <img
                        class="title-media"
                        src="/assets/kubernetes-ckad.avif"
                        alt="CKAD certification badge"
                        loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async"
                    />
                    <h4>CKAD — Certified Kubernetes Application Developer</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">Linux Foundation / CNCF · Kubernetes</p>
                <p>
                    Certification focused on developing and deploying
                    applications in Kubernetes — covering pods, deployments,
                    configuration, observability, and troubleshooting in
                    real-world environments.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="key" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>OAuth2 Authentication Services</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    FinanceFair & iptiQ (Swiss Re) · Java · Spring Boot · OAuth2
                    · JWT
                </p>
                <p>
                    Implemented standalone authentication microservices for
                    distributed systems, issuing and verifying JWT bearer
                    tokens. Centralized security across services with OAuth2 to
                    host in-house security.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="cloud" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>Cloud Migration & CI/CD Modernization</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">FinanceFair · AWS · GitHub Actions</p>
                <p>
                    Led the migration of the platform from Azure to AWS while
                    modernizing the delivery pipeline. Replaced Jenkins with
                    GitHub Actions to streamline deployments, improve
                    reliability, and enhance overall developer productivity.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="server" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>Kafka Streaming</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    iptiQ (Swiss Re) · Java · Spring Boot · Kafka
                </p>
                <p>
                    Designed and implemented Kafka-based event streaming to
                    capture and route all system events into a centralized data
                    lake. This foundation enabled real-time partner
                    notifications.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="code" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>Distributed Platform</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    iptiQ (Swiss Re) · Java · Spring Boot · Kafka · DDD ·
                    Hexagonal · Event Driven
                </p>
                <p>
                    Designed and built distributed microservices using
                    event-driven architecture, Domain-Driven Design, and
                    Hexagonal patterns. Delivered robust, testable services with
                    comprehensive unit and integration testing to support
                    mission-critical insurance operations.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="code" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>double-entry bookkeeping engine</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    FinanceFair · Java · Spring Boot · Kafka · PostgreSQL
                </p>
                <p>
                    Built a double-entry bookkeeping engine that powered
                    financial operations across the entire company. Delivered a
                    banking-grade ledger system enabling finance teams to manage
                    transactions with full accuracy and reliability directly
                    from the platform.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="ai" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>AI MCP Integration Layer</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    iptiQ (Swiss Re) · AI Integration · AWS Bedrock · MCP ·
                    Analytics
                </p>
                <p>
                    Integrated MCPO (Model Context Protocol OpenAPI compatible)
                    into the platform, enabling natural language queries across
                    tools like Grafana, Prometheus, Elasticsearch, Jira, and
                    Confluence. This AI-powered integration allows quick
                    insights and multi-source data analysis without requiring
                    deep technical expertise.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li class="project-card">
                <div class="project-title">
                    <span class="project-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <Icon icon="list" size="1.2em" />
                    </span>
                    <h4>Auction & Bidding System</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="project-meta">
                    FinanceFair · Java · Spring Boot · Kafka · PostgreSQL
                </p>
                <p>
                    Designed and developed engines to run daily auctions,
                    enabling automated (mandates) and manual bidding from
                    customers and seamless integration with the platform's core
                    financial services.
                </p>
            </li>
        </Grid>
    </div>
</section>
